{"tid":1938313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係返嚟嘅留學生 入嚟屌","createTime":"2020-03-22T12:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T06:36:28.000Z","uid":136967,"like":89,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb87e5f547a530a3dc20f27a17637b4b9450cc20","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"屋企人打香港嘅工 交香港嘅稅 <br />\n學費機票全部屋企攞出嚟 連政府UGC 四萬二都唔攞<br />\n有d直情中學就走咗 連本地教育資源都唔用<br />\n自己比錢出去增值自己(我讀醫療)之後返嚟貢獻香港<br />\n返嚟果下居然比人叫返香港&rdquo;搶&rdquo;資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我返嚟香港就係搶香港口罩 咁我一直留係香港呢半年唔洗戴嘅？<br />\n<br />\n留學生唔係個個老豆老母都高層高官富商<br />\n大把人好似我偉大嘅老豆老母咁 辛苦打工供我出去讀<br />\n留學就等於日日party嘅？自動pass架？<br />\n<br />\n自己嚴守緊14日 身邊識嘅返嚟都一樣<br />\n由機場開始全副武裝 全部坐的士返屋企之後無出過街<br />\n老實講留學生中招仲安全過香港人中招 <br />\n我地day 1已經有無病都強制隔離緊 有咩事直接拉埋入醫院生人勿近 <br />\n香港人中咗招潛伏期入面接觸嘅人一定係留學生幾十倍<br />\n仲要又行山又出街食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有話留學生無做過野果班黃納粹 <br />\n係阿你阿 無食過彈無流過血都唔當黃果d<br />\n當攬炒團隊係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩泥膠？自己搞外國遊行圍威喂？<br />\n話留學生淨係識IG po兩句 我做過d嘅野唔通又放哂上IG？<br />\n姑勿論我身邊一堆人上個暑假日日出街<br />\n留學生英美澳由七八月開始無停過整文宣簽聯署join議員<br />\n國際戰線呢四隻字你估淨係開po打飛機？背後幾多付出你知唔知？"},{"pid":"634d84da977e11e9e7058f95732d26d55ab7ff9e","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"留學生咁多人實有幾件港豬 實有幾件老豆老母係員佐狗 高官<br />\n就好似黃絲入面一定有幾件批鬥嘅黃納粹咁<br />\n又要返嚟又要剪手帶果d我恥與爲伍<br />\n但係希望唔好一竹篙打一船人<br />\n大部分留學生當香港喺屋企 同未來做嘢嘅地方<br />\n我地唔係外國人 有事返嚟香港暫避<br />\n我地係一班香港人 暫時去咗外國讀書<br />\n利申留學生 英藉 一樣諗住返香港做"},{"pid":"ab85c2bb77aab0e89d7a9471d5cfd22267cd961c","tid":1938313,"uid":2419,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/532vDWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F532vDWe.png&h=4a09026f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好明顯有堆人係咁開post帶風向分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471155de213a10b12910b33aa1754072e4d1a1d8","tid":1938313,"uid":96158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"你係英國返泥？ 其實而加果邊情況點 係咪真係asian行出街都比人喊打？"},{"pid":"c36288133804f9238c47fc8d5269a650dac997ec","tid":1938313,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"係我我都會翻黎"},{"pid":"4f9fb263d4cdbd96d1322d8038ccbb8467f682ef","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"你自律乖既唔怪你<br />\n不過點解唔留係英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec433d229ed5abcb3639053c4c632fb4f32b1705","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"471155de213a10b12910b33aa1754072e4d1a1d8","tid":1938313,"uid":96158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"你係英國返泥？ 其實而加果邊情況點 係咪真係asian行出街都比人喊打？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"係英國 有d地方有<br />\n多數講嘢難聽d姐 未去到喐手"},{"pid":"dc1267c5120916cc7251f63eb27d5a69f429691b","tid":1938313,"uid":215501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁上心<br />\n網軍新風向黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實朋友一個都冇咁樣諗"},{"pid":"3d4de25a590170c49c1c5ba7f06eff8f98e09a72","tid":1938313,"uid":299360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"自律既真係唔應該批鬥 要鬧鬧唔自律既同支那政府 港共政府"},{"pid":"784a600800e9bd0ab5aa8e1d5f503872bcfbd669","tid":1938313,"uid":95,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗太介意連登仔講乜，始終網上面講野唔洗表露身份又唔洗為自己講既野負責任。<br />\n<br />\n返到黎乖乖地自我隔離十四日其實無問題。"},{"pid":"f13067515670c51836a57c30fde9ad32736d6053","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f9fb263d4cdbd96d1322d8038ccbb8467f682ef","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"你自律乖既唔怪你<br />\n不過點解唔留係英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"d人唔識驚 個個hea洗下手算<br />\n識驚果d又唔識正確防疫 淨係一味搶廁紙搶意粉<br />\nthey are not worried<br />\nthat's worries me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc4d04570460c1c0cbd5a3e41b7a7ac283f3530","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13067515670c51836a57c30fde9ad32736d6053","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f9fb263d4cdbd96d1322d8038ccbb8467f682ef","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"你自律乖既唔怪你<br />\n不過點解唔留係英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"d人唔識驚 個個hea洗下手算<br />\n識驚果d又唔識正確防疫 淨係一味搶廁紙搶意粉<br />\nthey are not worried<br />\nthat's worries me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"Blow Jobson <br />\n唔係已經叫勤洗手咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6669be61b6628bdcf9a196fd5751b9f597875a08","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dc4d04570460c1c0cbd5a3e41b7a7ac283f3530","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13067515670c51836a57c30fde9ad32736d6053","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f9fb263d4cdbd96d1322d8038ccbb8467f682ef","tid":1938313,"uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"你自律乖既唔怪你<br />\n不過點解唔留係英國<i