>\nEven你有做文宣，國際線<br />\n加上香港人守咗個幾兩個月先守得住<br />\n你地一翻嚟就急增<br />\n正常都會忟憎嘅 唔好太放上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"唔少留學生由此至終都係真香港人<br />\n一路有跟貼香港 有錢出錢有力出力<br />\n無事嘅時侯就話外國手足打國際戰線著晒火又盛<br />\n有事嘅時候手足返黎就俾人話做少少嘢返黎避難<br />\n其實好打擊軍心"},{"pid":"a154b3e6aec0a19b070cc87a13b8fafb6af30a23","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200323/DDM3UGVPHB63DFSOBYV6MTLNEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200323%2FDDM3UGVPHB63DFSOBYV6MTLNEQ%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=fabd8d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200323%2FDDM3UGVPHB63DFSOBYV6MTLNEQ%2F&h=951773cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200323/DDM3UGVPHB63DFSOBYV6MTLNEQ/</a><br />\n【英國疫慌●倫敦直擊】港女燒足七天疑染疫 被拒檢測治療淪人球在家「等死」<br />\n仲可以話人地有事鐘無艷<br />\n吹風果d就預咗 跟埋風批鬥人自私果d<br />\n真係矇撚咗矇撚埋右"},{"pid":"e43aa093ddfbb0f67fd2b712b947d926e9f0af16","tid":1938313,"uid":63300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:22:47.000Z","msg":"連登多咗好多五毛帶風向，想分化啲人，唔洗咁上心"}],"pinned":{"pid":"19b200d528650c1e27c2ca9e1e2a23828518fa02","tid":1938313,"uid":136967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"留學生同外地港人返屋企就有人出嚟話自私<br />\n只係諗自己安危健康<br />\n唔諗其他安守本份香港人難道就好撚慷慨？"}}